featured_reviews.review_id:
One of the Old Mosques in Chickballapur. It has good parking facility during regular days as cars can be parked inside the Eidgah space.

The Imam, during time of review 2021, is good and polite. He has beautiful recitation and Masha Allah supports the Musallees for any queries related to Islam.

The Mosque, is peaceful. It is clean and well maintained. It is well ventilated. It has RO water drinking facility. It has a mirror. Also, there is toilet facility.

The Mosque is besides the Muslim Makkaan, also, this is a Mosque with an attached Eidgah to it.
